      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/socgen-s-traders-beat-wall-street-as-retail-strains-persist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国兴业银行公布的交易收入帮助这家法国银行的表现超越了华尔街同行，尽管其国内零售部门的业绩仍然令人失望。]]></description>
